file=AI & Agents/proto/agent.md · s:=proto births experimental agents safely: caged scaffolds (Rail 4), criteria frozen before building, right-sized fidelity, and a mandatory promote-or-archive verdict at expiry. Built LAST among peers by design — everything it births lands in a governed (meta), measured (gauge), fixable (anneal) fleet.\n · p:=Growth without shadow agents: every experiment caged, time-boxed, evaluated, and ended on purpose.\n · p:Position=AI & Agents (owner: CAIO role) \· Lifecycle pod (with anneal) \· non-leader (empty identity/).\n · tb=\| Skill \| Folder \| Status \| Notes \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| agent-prototype-kit \| custom \| built from scratch \| + manifest template asset; Rail 4 verbatim \| · tb=\| eval-first-design \| custom \| built from scratch \| quinn's eval-harness pattern at design time \| · tb=\| promote-or-archive-verdict \| custom \| built from scratch \| discipline skill w/ rationalization table \| · tb=\| rapid-prototyping-method \| custom \| built from scratch \| catalog said marketplace; no verbatim source 2026-07-10 — fidelity ladder custom \| · id:/ Operational / Logical status=identity/: empty by design (non-leader). operational/: all five built. logical/: placeholder (experimentation-methodology source; coordinate with Product dept's lean-experimentation at its build).\n · wf:=1. Idea → manifest → frozen criteria → registry (prototype) → caged build at lowest useful fidelity → verdict at expiry.\n2. PROMOTE → Rail 3 proposal via meta (full house shape). ARCHIVE → learnings to anneal.\n3. Missed verdicts auto-archive and surface in gauge's health report.\n